                      <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                          <locus from="1r" to="222r"/>
                          <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2400Talmid">Talmid</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>

                          <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">                               
                              <locus target="#222r"/>
                              ተፈጸመ፡ በዝየ፡ በ፷፻ወ፩፻፶ወ፰ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በወርኃ፡ ጥቅምት፡ አመ፡ ፱ለሠረቀ፡ ሌሊት፡ እም፲ወ፭ሠረቀ፡ መዓልት፡ በ፴ወ፫ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ 
                              ለንጉሥነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4015Fasilada">ፋሲለደስ፡</persName> በ፪ዓመት፡ በክህነተ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6071Krestodo">አቡነ፡ ክርስቶዶሉ፡</persName> በዘመነ፡ 
                              ማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ። ዘአብኡሰ፡ ዘንተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ኀበ፡ <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0329DE">ደብረ፡ ዳጋ፡ አቡነ፡ እስጢፋኖስ፡</placeName>
                              ወጽሐፊሁኒ፡ <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14482YekunoAmlak">ይኵኖ፡ አምላክ።</persName>
                              <note>Edited in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MZC4PZ7D"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1914Notice"/><title level="m">Notice sur les manuscrits éthiopiens de la Collection d’Abbadie</title><title level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</title><author><forename>Carlo</forename><surname>Conti Rossini</surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Imprimerie nationale</publisher><date>1914</date><series><title level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</title></series><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1914Notice</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1914Notice</note><citedRange unit="page">158-159</citedRange></bibl>.
                                  The date 15 Tǝqǝmt 6158 according to the Era of Grace appears to be mistaken (equivalent to 
                                  <date calendar="creation" when-custom="6158" when="0665">12 October 665</date>?). 
                                  The second year of the priesthood of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6071Krestodo">ʾabuna Krǝstodolu</persName> and
                                  the 33rd year of the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4015Fasilada">King Fāsiladas</persName>
                                  result in 1665 (CE). The colophon mentions the scribe <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14482YekunoAmlak">Yǝkʷǝnno ʾAmlāk</persName>
                                  and appears to tell that the exemplar of the manuscript (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾabʾu</foreign>) originates from <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0329DE">Dabra Dāgā ʾƎsṭifānos</placeName>.
                              It is not fully clear whether C. Conti Rossini considers the colophon as referring to the work or to the manuscript only (but the last 
                              would contradict to his 19th-century dating of the manuscript).
                              M. Chaîne tacitly corrects the colophon to <date> the year of grace 7158 = 1665 CE</date> 
                                  and considers it as the production year of the manuscript.
                                  </note>
                          </colophon>                          
